Value: Should the US impose higher taxes on the wealthy?
I absolutely think that the US should impose higher taxes on the wealthy
<lowercase>Totally agree! It seems fair to ask those who've benefited the most to contribute a bit more, right?</lowercase>​
Exactly, i think the divide between the middle class and the wealthy is so large, that it feels unfair to not tax the rich much more
<lowercase>Right? The gap just keeps growing. It makes sense to use that money to help bridge that divide. What kind of programs do you think would benefit the most from this?</lowercase>​
Considering where I live, I would say the homeless population should be the first group to receive aid from taxing the rich
